isis.stitle: ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - LUBRICATION, SEALERS AND MAINTENANCE INTERVALS - AXLE-REAR

item.para: Add 2 pints (0.946 liter) of forward rear axle differential capacity total to inter-axle differential.
Add an additional 2 pints (0.946 liter) of gear lubricant to inter-axle differential forward rear axle.
Add 1 pint (0.47 liter) of this total at pinion cage plug on single or tandem rear axles.
Fill forward rear and rear axle through fill hole located on side of carrier housing.
